nodes.text: Fufuneek was an Ewok of Bright Tree Village on the forest moon of Endor.

Fufuneek attacked the foot of an AT-ST during the Battle of Endor. He helped man an Ewok catapult and later, with the help of four other Ewoks, ambushed a group of stormtroopers who had pinned down Han Solo, Leia Organa, C-3PO, and R2-D2 at the Endor shield generator bunker.
